data.description:
Welcome to your dream oasis nestled on 3.6 acres of serene countryside, just outside the bustling city limits. This magnificent 3615 sq ft house is located on a tranquil dead end road, offering you the utmost privacy and tranquility.

As you step inside, you will be captivated by the spaciousness of this home. With an open floor plan, the main house boasts ample room for comfortable living. The living area features large windows that flood the space with natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The well-appointed kitchen is a chef's delight, complete with modern appliances, sleek countertops, and plenty of storage space.

Adjacent to the main house, an attached mother-in-law suite awaits, providing a perfect solution for multi-generational families or as a potential rental opportunity. This private suite offers a separate entrance, a cozy bedroom, a full bathroom, and a fully equipped kitchenette, ensuring a comfortable and independent living space.

Outside, you will find a detached storage shed, perfect for housing your tools, equipment, or even converting into a workshop. The fenced yard surrounding the property offers a secure space for children or pets to play freely, while you can relax and soak in the tranquil atmosphere.

With 3.6 acres of land, the possibilities are endless. Create your own private garden, set up a playground for the little ones, or simply enjoy the expansive green space as you indulge in outdoor activities with family and friends.

Located just a few minutes south of the interstate, this property allows you to enjoy the best of both worlds - the peacefulness of rural living combined with easy access to urban amenities. Whether you're seeking a peaceful retreat or a spacious home for a growing family, this property offers it all.

Don't miss out on this rare opportunity to own a sprawling 3615 sq ft house with an attached mother-in-law suite, a detached storage shed, and a fenced yard on 3.6 acres of pristine land. Schedule your private tour today and start envisioning the endless possibilities that await you in this idyllic haven.

Buyer's and buyers agent to verify all info.
